# $name

AiSOC **enricher** plugin generated by `aisoc plugin new`.

Enrichers add context to in-flight events. They are called by the orchestrator
once per matching event and must:

- Be fast (sub-second). Set `timeout_seconds` low.
- Be side-effect-free.
- Never raise on a miss — return `{}` instead.

## Develop

```bash
# Validate the manifest
aisoc plugin validate plugin.yaml

# Run unit tests once you add them
pytest -v
```

## Publish

```bash
aisoc plugin publish .
```

See the [AiSOC plugin docs](https://github.com/beenuar/AiSOC/tree/main/apps/docs/docs/plugins)
for the full lifecycle.
